弗兰克·卡特和性手枪表演帮助确保伦敦布什大厅的未来https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-sex-pistols-london-bush-hall-3779738?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=frank-carter-sex-pistols-london-bush-hallAneesa Ahmed Wed, 31 Jul 2024 15:52:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3779738 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗兰克·卡特和性手枪乐队的格伦·马特洛克、保罗·库克和史蒂夫·琼斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是在这座历史悠久的场馆的未来受到威胁之后发生的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-sex-pistols-london-bush-hall-3779738">Frank Carter &amp; Sex Pistols 展示的帖子有助于确保伦敦布什大厅的未来，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗兰克·卡特和性手枪乐队的格伦·马特洛克、保罗·库克和史蒂夫·琼斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_frankcarter_sexpistolsv2_press_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-carter">弗兰克·卡特 (Frank Carter)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sex-pistols">性手枪乐队 (Sex Pistols)</a>在伦敦布什大厅 (Bush Hall) 的演出门票全部售完，这将有助于确保这个标志性独立场地的未来。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-sex-pistols-paul-cook-3343927">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ – Sex Pistols 的保罗·库克</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-and-sex-pistols-announce-plans-to-play-never-mind-the-bollocks-in-its-entirety-3761808">弗兰克·卡特将与格伦·马特洛克、保罗·库克和史蒂夫·琼斯一起演奏整首《Never Mind The Bollocks》，</a>为历史悠久的牧羊人丛林场地筹集资金。</p><p>他们原本计划演出两晚，但在 8 月 13 日和 14 日的演出很快就售完后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sex-pistols-and-frank-carter-announce-extra-london-never-mind-the-bollocks-show-3763755">他们在 8 月 15 日增加了第三场演出</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sex-pistols-tickets/artist/874727?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=yp52H5zTtxyKRXXX38zZoRdjUkCzxpxMb0qcyU0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到剩余的门票。</a></p><p>现在，由于一些众筹和这些即将举行的演出的成功，伦敦独立场馆正在继续为未来几个月制定计划。 “Never Mind The Bollocks”演出的所有收益都用于帮助该场馆的长期文化输出。</p><p>在此之前，该场馆的未来已经受到关注，近几个月来，它永久关闭的可能性似乎越来越大。例如，今年早些时候，该公司透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/crowdfunder-launched-to-save-live-music-at-londons-legendary-bush-hall-3595570">需要通过众筹筹集 42,000 英镑，</a>以防止失去音乐地位。 </p><figure id="attachment_3779819" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3779819" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3779819" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Frank Carter &amp; The Rattlesnakes 乐队的 Frank Carter 将于 2024 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Frank-Carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3779819" class="wp-caption-text"> Frank Carter &amp; The Rattlesnakes 乐队的 Frank Carter 将于 2024 年演出。图片来源：Matt Jelonek/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Bush Hall 去年的现场音乐预订量下降了 24.5%。该场馆的董事总经理兼共同所有人查理·拉沃斯 (Charlie Raworth) 表示：“我们非常高兴布什音乐厅能够继续其作为深受喜爱的现场音乐和活动场所的传统。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这只有在我们社区和团队的大力支持下才可能实现。我们现在可以充满信心地为未来几年的音乐编程。”</p><p>该网站还与 Sugar &amp; Rind 和 Fightback Lager 公司建立了新的合作伙伴关系——每售出一品脱啤酒，这两家公司都会将一部分利润捐赠给基层场所——以保持大门敞开。</p><p>谈到这座历史悠久的场馆受到威胁时，卡特在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/download">2024 年下载节</a>上接受<em>NME</em>采访时表示，支持布什大厅等草根场馆是他一直以来最关心的事业。</p><p> “对我来说，始终支持草根场馆很重要，”卡特解释道。 “但现在，这种情况最为普遍，因为他们对政府感到非常失望。没有艺术资助。没有为艺术发生的地方提供资金。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这些空间不仅对娱乐、影响年轻音乐家和为新一代乐队提供去处很重要，而且对社区也很重要。这是我们所看到的在保守党政府统治下被彻底消除的主要事情之一。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C8UcK-mvEYA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-s