rcury-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/english_teacher_mercury-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a>宣布今晚（7 月 31 日）将在利兹举办一场特别的一次性免费家乡表演，以庆祝他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">获得水星奖</a>提名。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="358" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-mercury-prize-2024-interview-beyonce-new-album-3778358"><b>英语老师获得水星奖：“克服困难是值得的”</b></a></li></ul><p>乐队在社交媒体上宣布，该演出将与 Fender 合作在该市的 Brudenell Social Club 举行。晚上 7 点开始营业，乐队已确认先到先得。</p><p>这支独立乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-check-out-the-shortlisted-nominees-here-3777869">上周（7 月 25 日）获得了水星奖的认可</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785">前<i>NME</i>封面明星</a>的广受好评的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">“This Could Be Texas”</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">Ghetts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party 等</a>唱片一起入围。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corinne-bailey-rae">科琳·贝利·雷 (Corinne Bailey Rae)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">贝丝·吉本斯 (Beth Gibbons)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">巴里不会游泳</a>等。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">明天将在<a href="https://twitter.com/Nath_Brudenell?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Nath_Brudenell</a>与<a href="https://twitter.com/Fender?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Fender</a>合作举办免费入场演出，庆祝这一重大消息</p><p>晚上 7 点，先到先得 xxxxx <a href="https://t.co/u48k7KomqE">pic.twitter.com/u48k7KomqE</a></p><p> — 英语老师 (@Englishteac_her) <a href="https://twitter.com/Englishteac_her/status/1818245522966069309?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>收到这一消息后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-mercury-prize-2024-interview-beyonce-new-album-3778358">乐队向<i>《NME》</i>讲述了</a>获得提名的意义，女主唱莉莉·方丹 (Lily Fontaine) 将其形容为“精神上的”，并称今年的提名名单是“迄今为止最好的一年”。不仅仅是因为我们正在努力！” </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="357" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785"><b>封面上的英语老师：来自英国吉他音乐中心的重要声音</b></a></li></ul><p>对于一支<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-case-has-been-made-for-a-1-ticket-levy-on-all-arena-gigs-for-the-survival-of-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3611533">一直直言不讳地表达艺术家在当前环境下生存和发展是多么困难的</a>乐队来说，英语老师说这种荣誉感更加深刻。</p><p> “有很多诱惑让你不继续创作音乐，因为你身体上不能，”方丹承认。 “我们必须经历很多事情才能真正制作这张专辑。它以这种奇怪的文化认可的方式得到了回报，所以值得度过困难时期。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C92pA9Wo0-H/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=lo